  PRODUCT DESCRIPTION

                           Intuit TurboTax Premier 2008

   This is a hybrid disk, works on both pc and mac!

   If you own stocks, bonds, mutual funds, or rental property, TurboTax
   Premier makes it easy to keep more money in your pocket.

   Everything you need to easily do your simple tax return - designed to help
   you make the most of your investments and rental property deductions, so
   you get the biggest tax refund possible.

   Gets your W-2 and 1099 data directly from over 100,000 participating
   employers and financial institutions; transfers info from last year&#039;s
   TurboTax return to this year&#039;s.

   Searches for more than 350 deductions, including mortgage interest,
   education, and medical expenses, to get you the biggest refund -
   guaranteed.

   Provides extra guidance for investment sales such as stocks, bonds,
   mutual funds, and employee stock plans.



  INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

   1. Unrar, Burn or mount with Daemon Tools.

   2. Install and enjoy :)
